name: CancerBenignOrBorderlineCNSTumorsDisordersSNOMED
title: Cancer [Benign or Borderline CNS Tumors] (Disorders) (SNOMED)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses or problems that represent that the patient has Cancer [Benign or Borderline CNS Tumors] regardless of the clinical presentation of the condition. This corresponds to the 2021 NPCR Expanded List for Cancer Reporting, subset to Benign or Borderline CNS tumors.),(Data Element Scope: Diagnoses or problems documented in a clinical record.),(Inclusion Criteria: Cancer (Benign or Borderline CNS Tumors)),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
